Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the voice of God cases under I have heard the voice of God this name was scrawled there by the murderer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's the spirit a couple murder case
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Since both of them drowned that case seem to be unrelated to the others
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But the name of the killer given by the Japanese Doctor Who was the only witness in that case was the same
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the same name in every case
